text: Kalletal is a municipality in the Lippe district of North Rhine-Westphalia, Germany, with c. 13,800 inhabitants (2013). ==Comprising villages (Ortschaften)== * Asendorf * Bavenhausen * Bentorf * Brosen * Erder * Heidelbeck * Henstorf * Hohenhausen * Kalldorf * Langenholzhausen * Lüdenhausen * Osterhagen * Stemmen * Talle * Tevenhausen * Varenholz * Westorf == References == ==External links== * Official website Category:Towns in North Rhine-Westphalia Category:Lippe Category:Principality of Lippe
title: Kalletal
